  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 63-16-13, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO INCREASE BY A CERTAIN AMOUNT THE FINE FOR A CONVICTION OF OPERATING A MOTOR VEHICLE WITHOUT MANDATORY LIABILITY INSURANCE; TO PROVIDE THAT A JUDGE SHALL NOT WAIVE SUCH FINE AND MAY AUTHORIZE THE REINSTATEMENT OF A DEFENDANT'S DRIVER'S LICENSE ONLY UPON PROOF OF MANDATORY LIABILITY INSURANCE AND PAYMENT OF ANY FINES, ASSESSMENTS AND/OR FEES; TO AMEND SECTION 63-15-4, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO CONFORM; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
